df9f6897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西班牙文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MbqNbu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MbqNbu&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=73150c73\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MbqNbu</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2x7YQMm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2x7YQMm.png&h=d3cb1350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRetweet / comment / 加hashtag <br />\n及手足互科</span><br />\n<br />\n大家快做其他語言tweet <br />\n如徳 意 韓 瑞典挪威波蘭<br />\n印尼<br />\n<br />\n放此俾人retweet！"},{"pid":"356ff5dff55b023257e851bae0507e5287aa14c9","tid":1789561,"uid":208122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:35:36.000Z","msg":"光復香港由港足做起<br />\n<br />\nWe are Hong Kong 🇭🇰🇭🇰🇭🇰<br />\nOle ole ole<br />\n<br />\n本谷旨在想有興趣睇港足港超或者一路有睇開的球迷入嚟一齊討論傾下波經。以老帶新，由資深球迷帶新手球迷入門，交換資訊，降低香港睇波門檻，等愈來愈多球迷入場撐港足，重建香港球巿。<br />\n<br />\n入group嘅可以講低自己中意邊隊，得閒約埋一齊去睇波。仲等咩快d入嚟<br />\n<br />\n光復香港由重建港足文化開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=683d7426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ</a>"},{"pid":"30b0f71f30f2482890ae5e8d89253709297f5942","tid":1789561,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:36:01.000Z","msg":"自推，順便宣傳<br />\n<br />\n眾籌Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/free-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Ffree-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition%2F&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=a75ef0b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/free-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition/</a>"},{"pid":"7f6a72f07bb54c8a4d3ff77f7cd00dbe1cd1c429","tid":1789561,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco